<DOC><DOCNO> WSJ870529-0024 </DOCNO><HL> Business Brief:Federated Department Stores Inc.</HL><DD> 05/29/87</DD><SO> WALL STREET JOURNAL (J)</SO><IN> FDS </IN><TEXT>   FEDERATED DEPARTMENT STORES INC. said holders approved a doubling of authorized common to 400 million shares. The Cincinnati retailer said the increase will maintain the flexibility for growth it had before a 2-for-1 stock split paid May 11. </TEXT></DOC>